Corporal Mark Donaldson VC was awarded the Victoria Cross for his bravery in Afghanistan in 2008 . 
  He claims to have shot a Taliban warlord who boasted he would kill Prince Harry . 
  The prince is headed for his final tour of duty in the elite SAS headquarters in Perth . 
  Corporal Donaldson was part of a unit ordered to assassinate the warlord codenamed Javelin on his first tour of Afghanistan . 
  In 2012 the Taliban threatened to 'eliminate' the royal heir . 
  Donaldson is one of Australia's most highly decorated soldiers . 
 